Interface ISubGradleProjectConfig

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IBundleGradleProjectConfig, IRuntimeGradleProjectConfig, IWebGradleProjectConfig
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BundleGradleProjectConfig, RuntimeGradleProjectConfig, SubGradleProjectConfig, WebGradleProjectConfig

    public interface ISubGradleProjectConfig
    Configuration for an Xtext sub-project, analogous to SubProjectConfig.
